data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers 2,285 SF of open concept living space. The family room features custom lighting and surround sound, connecting seamlessly to the kitchen with ample cabinets and a butler's pantry leading to the formal dining room. Interior finish work includes crown molding, upgraded baseboards, and more. Upstairs, you'll find 4 bedrooms, including a spacious master with an en-suite bathroom. The backyard is a paradise with a patio, outdoor speakers, an above-ground pool, fruit trees, and extra storage space. The home is on a large lot in a cul-de-sac with easy access to shopping and major highways, and there's no HOA. Don't miss the walking trail and ravine nearby!
